The paper deals with the security and safety of implantable medical devices, which involves aspects of cryptography, human-computer interaction, information theory, systems and control, and cybernetics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
